'''小安東尼歐·薩巴托'''（{{lang-en|Antonio Sabàto Jr.}}，{{bd|1972年|2月29日}}）是一位義大利裔[[美國|美國]]的演員和模特。他出生在義大利<ref name="ewref">{{cite news |last=Carter|first=Alan|title=Raising TV's Pulse Rate | publisher = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 1993-04-23 | url = http://ew.com/article/1993/04/23/antonio-sabato-daytimes-new-hunk/ | accessdate = 2017-02-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161024041450/http://www.ew.com/article/1993/04/23/antonio-sabato-daytimes-new-hunk}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/access/1513855091.html?dids=1513855091:1513855091&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jul+21%2C+2008&author=FRANK+LOVECE&pub=Newsday+(Combined+editions)&desc=REALITY+CHECK&pqatl=google |first=Frank |last=Lovece |title=Reality Check |date=2008-07-21 |work=Newsday}}</ref>，成長在美國。他因擔任[[卡爾文·克雷恩|CK]]模特和出演肥皂劇《[[杏林春暖|杏林春暖]]》（General Hospital）而成名。他也參加過一些真人秀節目的演出。2016年，他支持[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]競選美國總統<ref>Jonathan, Robert. "[http://www.inquisitr.com/2976124/antonio-sabato-jr-trump-and-cruz/ Antonio Sabato Jr. sounds off on Trump and Cruz] {{Wayback|url=http://www.inquisitr.com/2976124/antonio-sabato-jr-trump-and-cruz/ |date=20201010200259 }}." Inquisitr. 2016-04-08. Retrieved 2016-07-17.</ref>並且在[[2016年共和黨全國大會|2016年共和黨全國大會]]上發表演說<ref name="APTebowRumor">[http://www.seattletimes.com/nation-world/more-establishment-than-celebrity-in-trump-convention-lineup/ Tim Tebow: Speaking slot at Trump convention 'a rumor'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.seattletimes.com/nation-world/more-establishment-than-celebrity-in-trump-convention-lineup/ |date=20201107091157 }}, Associated Press (July 14, 2016).</ref>。

